data.name: Oracle Cards
data.description: A JSON file containing one Scryfall card object for each Oracle ID on Scryfall. The chosen sets for the cards are an attempt to return the most up-to-date recognizable version of the card.

data.name: Unique Artwork
data.description: A JSON file of Scryfall card objects that together contain all unique artworks. The chosen cards promote the best image scans.

data.name: Default Cards
data.description: A JSON file containing every card object on Scryfall in English or the printed language if the card is only available in one language.

data.name: All Cards
data.description: A JSON file containing every card object on Scryfall in every language.

data.name: Rulings
data.description: A JSON file containing all Rulings on Scryfall. Each ruling refers to cards via an `oracle_id`.
